title: Denver's defense leads Broncos past Vikings 23-20 (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,071 Denver's defense leads Broncos past Vikings 23-20 (Yahoo Sports) DENVER (AP) -- Brandon McManus kicked a 39-yard field goal with 1:51 left and Denver had seven sacks in the Broncos' 23-20 win over the Minnesota Vikings on Sunday.
